gujarati.context:
Say say say someone's ear; 
One only is without bounds;

But whatever comes to my knowledge, I'll speak out its praise.

This which was done nothing, some gain; 
This world's connection gone, it came; 
That is the name of my father and brother, it became weak in this body.

Here is the translation:

He came to meet his end, being worn out by intense heat; 
Many tribes are with you, O Lord, and every moment is blissful.

Here is the translation:

This has been done by Jagdish, learned yoga in the company; 
Hari says it's his time to eat, and this hungry one should be fed.

Here is the translation:

Done mercy to merciful one, earned eternal life eternal eternal;
Lord manifest has made assembly, gone seeing sight divine divine;
